headline: Jacobs Selected to Design Light Rail Extension in Seattle
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected to provide design services for Sound Transit's West Seattle Link Extension. This project will expand Seattle's light rail network, enhancing connectivity for residential and economic centers, and offering faster, more reliable service.
